<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 shén jiàn lì de jiào huì tā bì fù zé, yīn jiān de quán bǐng bù néng shèng guò.
 shén jiàn lì de jiào huì tā bì fù zé, tā yào chú miè yī qiè yì duān xié shuō.
 tā yào jiàn lì yī qún zàn měi de zi mín, wàn guó de zhēn bǎo dōu bì yùn lái.
 lí míng qián de hēi àn jí jiāng guò qù, yào xiāng xìn shén yào qīn zì fù xìng tā de zuò wèi.</lyrics>
